{
  "text": "The force from the surface, F S , can be expressed as F S = J I \u00d7 \u03c6 0\u1e91 , where J I is the image antivortex contribution to the total vortex current J V+I . The calculation of J V+I can also be carried out by using the conformal mapping from the w-plane to the \u03b6-plane (see Appendix C). The components of J V+I are given by [CITATION_1] ",
  "correct_citation": {
